<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_93_r3l6"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als wir nehſt 
<del rend="strikethrough"> beÿ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1583232106900_288">cʒü </ab></add> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit ge 
<del rend="strikethrough"> habt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_r3l5">ſchıkt </ab></add> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_r3l4">Hanſen </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l8">
<del rend="strikethrough">Pilſacher </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_93_r3l7"><expan>Newſtet<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> / vnd Hanſen Stecʒman / von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / als Hans <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l9"><expan>Lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> / geladen hat / <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> auf die <expan>Lantſchran<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>hirſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l10"> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſie vns vvol geſagt 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> / vvie Jr ew <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> <note place="interlinear"><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1576565635300_152">a </ab></note> gelimppflıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l11">beweiſet habt / des wir ew cʒemal <expan>fleiʒʒiklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> danken / vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l12">daʒ ewr <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / daʒ Jr die ſache mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>abtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> vvolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l13">vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm dar auf <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het </del> als die ſache <expan>geſchob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> was / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ au </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l14">cʒü <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> nehſten <expan>Lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> das nach Ostern würd / habt Jr <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>lantrıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l15"><expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ er das beſteen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüll . biʒ awſgeen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Pfingſtvvoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l16">Alſo ob 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr </del> des nicht <expan>abtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht / ſo vvolt Jr vns in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit einen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l17">tag <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> <note place="interlinear"><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1576565639215_157">b </ab></note> / . Nu <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr erberkeit <expan>fleiʒʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <note place="interlinear"><ab facs="#facs_93_line_1576565654646_173">c </ab></note> daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">an ew </del> vvıſſen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet wie es darvmb <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ / ob Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l19">das mit Jm <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / . vnd het Jr des mit Jm nicht <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l20">daʒ Jr <expan>beſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllet / ob Jr das noch mit Jm <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> möht / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l21">Mocht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des nicht geſein / daʒ Jr vns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> einen <expan>nemlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag ſecʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l22">vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreibt</expan> / So <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü ew ſchıcken / . Doch getrawen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l23">wir ew vvol / Jr tragt das ſüſt / ab / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>v<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_93_r3l24"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> / . <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> Anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
<note place="marginleft">
<ab facs="#facs_93_r1l1"><expan cert="medium">R<ex>ecipimus</ex></expan>
<expan cert="medium">T<ex>utis</ex></expan></ab>
</note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_93" id="46r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von <expan>Gumppemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                        marschalk, <expan>Bering<ex>er</ex></expan> Hale, Wielant Swelher und
                        Seiczen Marschalk </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als wir nehst <add>czü</add>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit ge<add>schikt</add>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>Hansen</add>
<add><expan>Newstet<ex>er</ex></expan></add> und Hansen Steczman von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        als Hans <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>, geladen hat
                            <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> auf die <expan>lantschran<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        gen <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie uns
                        wol gesagt, wie ir ew <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<app>
<note place="interlinear">a</note>
</app> gelimppflich beweiset habt, des wir ew czemal
                                <expan>fleizziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> danken und
                                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz ewr
                            <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz ir die sache mit
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>abtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt. Und als die sache
                                <expan>geschob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> was czü
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> nehsten <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan>,
    das nach <app><note><q type="date">ostern</q>23.03.1410</note></app> würd, habt ir <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er das besteen
                                <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> süll biz awsgeen
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>pfingstwoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>11.05.1410</note></app>. Also ob des nicht
                                <expan>abtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht, so wolt ir uns in
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit einen tag
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan>. <app>
<note place="interlinear">b </note>
</app>Nu <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr erberkeit
                                <expan>fleizzikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <app>
<note place="interlinear">c </note>
</app> daz ir uns wissen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, wie es
                        darumb <expan>gelege<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, ob ir das mit im
                                <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> habt. Und het ir des mit im nicht
                                <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>beseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, ob ir das noch mit im
                                <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> möht. Mocht
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des nicht gesein, daz ir uns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> einen <expan>nemlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        tag seczt und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan>, so
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü ew
                        schicken. Doch getrawen wir ew wol, ir tragt das süst ab. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. <app>
<note place="marginleft">
<expan cert="medium">R<ex>ecipimus</ex></expan>
<expan cert="medium">t<ex>utis</ex></expan>. </note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
